{
  "texts": [
    "In this paper, eight companies' stock price from 01/05/2015 to 08/05/2024 are used, which include Apple (AAPL), Airbus (EADSY), HSBC (0005.HK), InfuSystem (INFU), Toyota (7203.T), Tencent (0700.HK), Pepsi (PEP), and Petrobras (PBR).The selected companies represent diverse financial markets and sectors.",
    "Apple is an American company renowned for its innovative software and electronic products.",
    "Airbus is a leading European aerospace company that designs, manufactures, and delivers commercial aircraft, helicopters, and defense systems.",
    "HSBC is a British banking and financial services company headquartered in London.",
    "InfuSystem Holdings is an American healthcare company specializing in integrated therapy services and medical equipment management."
  ]
}